《穷查理宝典》：要想拥有财富，必须先使自己配得上它

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appYDfMcMtV2307/a_5b44b9eae81d0_sHRB5IVY

<section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="line-height: 1.75; letter-spacing: 1.75px; padding: 0px 20px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: justify; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></strong></p></section></section></section><section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 1.75; letter-spacing: 2px; padding: 0px 20px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); line-height: 1.75; letter-spacing: 2px; padding: 0px 20px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">有人一年读杂书365本，有人一年只读10本同一主题的书。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">问，“谁的技能增长更快？”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">答案是，一年只读10本书的那位，因为主题阅读的效果不是以加法计算，而是以乘法计算。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">我们人类的大脑不擅长深入学习，但是天生就擅长找不同，即使没有完整的信息，只要信息足够多，信息之间的距离比较近，人脑也会自动脑补出它们之间的联系，一旦完成了知识与知识之间的脑补，这一大片知识日后就能随时随地地提取出来，帮你解决问题。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">主题阅读就是让你的大脑处在找不同的模式下，读第一本书的时候，你可能只领会了作者不足三成的思想；但是当你读第二本书的时候，奇妙的事情就发生了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">因为是同一主题，所以它们之间必然存在着千丝万缕地联系。这些联系就是我们学习、记忆和存储的线索，有了这些线索的帮助，你学习的效果会大大提高，这个时候你读完一本书，效果就会远超读第一本，很可能这时候你就能领会到多达七成的思想内核了。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">依次类推，一本本读下去，读到第10本书书的时候，你在读书时不仅能够轻松领会作者的思想，甚至还能发现作者的不足，边读书边创新，以至于读完一本书之后，你也在脑海中同时完成了一次创造。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">本专栏书籍解读人是冯冠军。</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">冯冠军 ，经济学博士、中国教育学会财商研究中心专家委员，</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">爱读书，尤其爱读经济学领域的相关书籍。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">为帮助大家快速入门经济学，冯老师特地为大家挑选了十本最简单易懂又不失专业水准地，经济学科普读物。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">他将带领大家由人物传记启程，由浅入深的对经济学现象抽丝剥茧，透过表象追寻经济学底层规律的脉络轨迹，最后以《市场的逻辑》收关，带您直面那双著名的“看不见地手”。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">整个主题阅读的旅程，就像是一个老司机带着您走了一条通往经济学殿堂的捷径，在这有限的篇幅与时间内，冯老师会力求最大程度上为您还原那个世界的全部美景。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;">这十本书分别是：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">1、《巴菲特传》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">2、《穷查理宝典》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">3、《富爸爸穷爸爸》</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style=